rows.label: qst003601_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, you must be the ones
Moui mentioned. Here to
join the Militia Corps?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0002
rows.name: Just here to help? That's a shame.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0003
rows.name: Very well, I'll tell you.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0004
rows.name:
The goods I ordered a while
ago haven't arrived at all.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0005
rows.name:
I ordered them from Mopopo
at the Uneri Root Camp in
Lower Gula, but...

rows.label: qst003601_msg0006
rows.name:
Until now, they've always delivered
within a few days of ordering... I'm
worried something may have happened.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0007
rows.name:
If they were attacked by
monsters, there's nothing
I could do if I went.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0008
rows.name:
That's why I asked Moui
to send someone strong.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0009
rows.name:
The Uneri Root Camp is at the Zain's
Waytree on the Goldoa Plain.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm sorry to ask, but could
you go check on the situation
at the Uneri Root Camp?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0011
rows.name: It'd be a great help. Thank you.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0101
rows.name:
The Uneri Root Camp is at the Zain's
Waytree on the Goldoa Plain.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0102
rows.name: I hope they're just running late...

rows.label: qst003601_msg0201
rows.name:
You're back. Was everything
alright? A fight with monsters...?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0202
rows.name:
What?! She didn't want to
deliver it because she
wouldn't get a service fee?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0203
rows.name: And you carried it here for her?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0204
rows.name: Oh my. I feel bad about that.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0205
rows.name: But thank you. That was a great help.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0206
rows.name:
I thought it was strangely
expensive... So that's where
the money was going...

rows.label: qst003601_msg0207
rows.name:
I don't want to add extra
money... What should I do...?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0208
rows.name: She wanted to eat some Ama-Ama Uinna?

rows.label: qst003601_msg0209
rows.name:
Come to think of it, Mopopo
always used to eat while walking
on her way home from work...

rows.label: qst003601_msg0210
rows.name:
I remember she'd always jump
at any new or popular dishes.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0211
rows.name: Alright, I've got it!

rows.label: qst003601_msg0212
rows.name:
I'll try to negotiate with her by
luring her with delicious food so
she'll continue to deliver for us.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0213
rows.name:
Yes, thank you very much.
That was a great help.

rows.label: qst003601_msg0214
rows.name:
I'll be sure to tell Moui that
you resolved this for us.
